sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant Frontend
    participant AuthAPI
    participant Database

    User->>Browser: Open login page
    Browser->>Frontend: GET /login
    Frontend-->>Browser: Render login form
    Browser-->>User: Show form

    User->>Browser: Enter email & password
    User->>Browser: Click "Sign in"
    Browser->>Frontend: POST /login (credentials)
    Frontend->>Frontend: Validate input

    alt Valid input
        Frontend->>AuthAPI: Authenticate(user, password)
        AuthAPI->>Database: Lookup user / verify hash
        Database-->>AuthAPI: User record
        AuthAPI->>AuthAPI: Verify password / create token
        AuthAPI-->>Frontend: JWT / session token
        Frontend-->>Browser: Set cookie / redirect to dashboard
        Browser-->>User: Show dashboard
    else Invalid credentials
        AuthAPI-->>Frontend: 401 Unauthorized
        Frontend-->>Browser: Error message
        Browser-->>User: Show "Invalid email or password"
    end
